folder: St. Marks Place & Nicholas Street, Staten Island, NY
original_title: Richmond: St. Marks Place - Nicholas Street
text:
St. Marks Place, north side, at Nicholas Street, showing the Wisteria Apartments (at No. 141) and the Castleton
Apartments.
March 29, 1930
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same, another view, as seen from the Curtis
High School grounds.
March 5, 1930
